    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You let your mind dive into the depths of your curse, transforming into an incredibly efficient killing machine. As your fur extends and your animalistic traits become more pronounced, you resemble a savage humanoid sage creature, almost like a werecreature.<br />If you already have Fervor active, this jutsu refreshes its duration and you must not pay the concentration on it anymore.<br />In addition to the bonuses from Fervor, you gain:</p><ul><li>2 ranks of Berserker that you do not lose while this jutsu remains active regardless of immunities to the condition.</li><li>+20 feet to your speed.</li><li>+4 to all Strength, Dexterity, and Constitution checks and saving throws.</li><li>+1d10 to all your attacks and Clan Hijutsu damages.</li><li>Every creature within sight of your transformation gains 1 rank of Hopeless.</li><li>Immunity to Charmed, Weakened, and Confused conditions while in this form.</li></ul><p>After this jutsu ends, you gain 2 ranks of Exhaustion, but you can only lose one rank of Exhaustion per long rest. You cannot lose this jutsu's concentration as the result of being attacked.</p>",
